# Ruby default gem CVEs — erb and net-imap ship with ruby:3.4.7-slim at vulnerable versions.
# These are default gems: gem update installs patched versions but cannot remove the original
# specifications/default/*.gemspec files that Trivy scans. The patched versions are present
# and active at runtime; the old gemspecs are stale artifacts of Ruby's default gem mechanism.
# Mitigation: RUN gem update erb net-imap --no-document in the Dockerfile final stage.
CVE-2026-41316
CVE-2026-42246
